snippet.title: AoTTG2 Devblog - Official Alpha Release!!
snippet.description:
It's been a long time since we last made a dev blog. Let's go over all the changes since we last got in touch and show off some of the new stuff we've added! 

DOWNLOAD AOTTG2!

https://aottg2.itch.io/aottg2

Join the Discord! https://discord.gg/J6EPdK4JpR

Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/aottg2/
Follow us on Twitter/X: https://x.com/aottg2
Follow us on TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@aottg2

Support the game on Patreon (NOTE: the money given to us on Patreon is only ever used to pay for the servers. We take none of it ourselves!): https://www.patreon.com/aottg2


Credits:
Editing: Artur Volosin, Thyme, BLuR
Footage: Confusion, Thyme, BLuR
Music: Dakros (Davin Chilly), Unrelated Acts, Nadim Doueiri, WarmMoistBeans
Credits for all development and assets are listed in-game.

AoTTG2 (Attack on Titan Tribute Game 2) is a volunteer-created fangame based on the game AoTTG (Attack on Titan Tribute Game) by Feng Lee.
